FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [b].[Id], [b].[ImageUrl], [b].[LinkUrl], [b].[Online], [b].[Title]
    FROM [Banners] AS [b]
    WHERE [b].[Id] = @__id_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [BannerStats] AS [b0] ON [t].[Id] = [b0].[FKBanner]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [b0].[Id]

SELECT [b2].[Title], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [b].[Hour]
    FROM [BannerStats] AS [b]
    WHERE [b2].[Id] = [b].[FKBanner]) AS [Hour], (
    SELECT COUNT(*)
    FROM [BannerStats] AS [b0]
    WHERE ([b2].[Id] = [b0].[FKBanner]) AND ([b0].[Event] = 2)) AS [ClickPerHour], (
    SELECT COUNT(*)
    FROM [BannerStats] AS [b1]
    WHERE ([b2].[Id] = [b1].[FKBanner]) AND ([b1].[Event] = 1)) AS [ImpressionPerHour]
FROM [Banners] AS [b2]

SELECT [b].[Title], [b].[Id] AS [BannerId], [b].[ClickPerHour], [b].[Hour], [b].[ImpressionPerHour]
FROM (
    select a.Id, a.Title, b.Hour,CONVERT(date, b.Date) [Date], (Select COUNT(*) from BannerStats where FKBanner = a.Id and Hour = b.Hour and Event = 2) as ClickSummary,
                    (Select COUNT(*) from BannerStats where FKBanner = a.Id and Hour = b.Hour and Event = 1) as ImpressionSummary  
                    from Banners a cross join BannerStats b group by hour,a.Id,Title, CONVERT(date, b.Date) order by Hour
) AS [b]
WHERE CONVERT(date, [b].[Date]) = @__date_Date_0

SELECT [b].[Title], [b].[Id] AS [BannerId], [b].[ClickPerHour], [b].[Hour], [b].[ImpressionPerHour]
FROM (
    select a.Id, a.Title, b.Hour,CONVERT(date, b.Date) [Date], (Select COUNT(*) from BannerStats where FKBanner = a.Id and Hour = b.Hour and Event = 2) as ClickSummary,
                    (Select COUNT(*) from BannerStats where FKBanner = a.Id and Hour = b.Hour and Event = 1) as ImpressionSummary

) AS [b]

SELECT [b].[Title], [b].[Id] AS [BannerId], [b].[ClickPerHour], [b].[Hour], [b].[ImpressionPerHour]
FROM (
    select a.Id, a.Title, b.Hour,CONVERT(date, b.Date) [Date], (Select COUNT(*) from BannerStats where FKBanner = a.Id and Hour = b.Hour and Event = 2) as ClickPerHour,
                    (Select COUNT(*) from BannerStats where FKBanner = a.Id and Hour = b.Hour and Event = 1) as ImpressionPerHour  
                    from Banners a cross join BannerStats b group by hour,a.Id,Title, CONVERT(date, b.Date)
) AS [b]
WHERE CONVERT(date, [b].[Date]) = @__date_Date_0
